{"tid":381411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機上演算微積分　經濟學教授被當恐怖份子","createTime":"2017-08-31T02:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T05:06:28.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78262a5a5169c49fec314886e341685fb92be542","tid":381411,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"美國一名大學經濟學教授，在飛機上演算複雜的數學公式，卻被鄰座一名女乘客懷疑是恐怖份子，遭帶離客機接受盤問。<br />\n賓州大學（University of Pennsylvania）經濟學教授孟思奧（Guido Menzio），原定周四（5日）搭乘美國航空AA3950班機由費城前往雪城（Syracuse），再赴加拿大安大略的皇后大學（Queen&rsquo;s University）參加學術研討。<br />\n<br />\n他在機位等候起飛時，於座位上演算一條微積分公式，但鄰座一名女乘客完全不認識這些數學符號，以為他在寫恐嚇字條，深感不安。女乘客於是謊稱身體不適要下機，等離開機艙後，她向空服員表示：「覺得孟思奧非常可疑，可能是恐怖份子，希望改搭另一架航班。」<br />\n機場為了安全起見，立刻派人將孟思奧帶下機。這名原籍義大利的大學教授得知被人當恐怖份子後，哭笑不得，但他配合調查。雖然孟思奧解釋後，很快就獲准重返客機，但客機仍較原定時間晚了兩個多小時才抵達目的地。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160508/855864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20160508%2F855864%2F&d=4dOpNOaat%2FznNFlMgXPY58mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=9a87deba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160508/855864/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOld news"},{"pid":"d2727dd4862b60ad22b70a1e724c348700e5a4d8","tid":381411,"uid":36494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:25:38.000Z","msg":"女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2719b3c91a0168c09874fbf0ecd2de920480da4","tid":381411,"uid":93986,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:31:28.000Z","msg":"Science bitch"},{"pid":"e02c1b93da82953e6229bf9e3146c6a70aa268c4","tid":381411,"uid":13115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:32:55.000Z","msg":"蠢女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482de0d6a0766074eaf99b48e2536c28466aea75","tid":381411,"uid":134864,"like":1,"di